data.description: High impact resistant roof with 30-50  year life expectance (which also equates to a substantial savings on home insurance premiums) Full house gutters, new master bathroom luxury vinyl flooring. No HOA. Single Story home offers a beautiful and spacious floor plan and landscaping, oversized mature treed lot and a 21x24 workshop with electric. Kitchen with lots of storage and counter space which opens to a large living room with fireplace and formal dining room that is perfect for entertaining.  Master bedroom with large ensuite bathroom with luxury plank flooring, garden tub. Secondary bedrooms are spacious with lots of closet space.  Fourth bedroom with french doors could be a second living room, game room or office.  Fully fenced yard with covered patio that opens up to a greenbelt in the rear of the property which gives more privacy.  Solar Screens to save on energy costs and a chicken coop and yard for sustainable living in a quiet neighborhood.
